form",[159,166,167],{},"korte social video’s en YouTube Shorts",[29,169,171],{"className":170},[37],"\nDoor consistente formats en storytelling groeide het YouTube-kanaal naar meer dan 214.000 totale weergaven, met meerdere video’s boven de 10.000 views.\n",[11,173,175],{"className":174},[42],[176,177],"shorts-grid",{":items":178},"[\n{\"title\":\"Wat is er nieuw aan de vernieuwde XPENG\",\"views\":\"17K views\",\"src\":\"\u002Fimages\u002Fother\u002Fxpeng_short.mp4\",\"href\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fshorts\u002F_V4ws5ELHSk\"},\n{\"title\":\"Volkswagen T-Roc review\",\"views\":\"2.3K views\",\"src\":\"\u002Fimages\u002Fother\u002Ftroc_short.mp4\",\"href\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fshorts\u002Frzi0D8OU230\"},\n{\"title\":\"Porsche in 60 seconden\",\"views\":\"1.4K views\",\"src\":\"\u002Fimages\u002Fother\u002Fporsche_short.mp4\",\"href\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fshorts\u002F0aPPirWCucQ\"}\n]",[11,180,182],{"className":181},[42],[183,184],"video-grid",{":videos":185},"[\n{\"title\":\"Auto Atlas video 1\",\"url\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002FhIWASu1xMjw?si=nsIM4m304FTTTO3O\"},\n{\"title\":\"Auto Atlas video 2\",\"url\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fwatch?v=s2qBp3iqnlk&t=1s\"}\n]",[11,187,189,196],{"className":188},[14,51],[11,190,192],{"className":191},[18],[20,193,195],{"id":194},"resultaat","Resultaat",[11,197,199],{"className":198},[27],[29,200,202],{"className":201},[32],"Het Auto Atlas project gaf mij de kans om een merk over meerdere jaren te helpen ontwikkelen en mijn vaardigheden in verschillende disciplines te combineren.",[11,204,207,216,224],{"className":205},[206],"case-kpis",[11,208,113,211],{"className":209},[210],"case-kpi",[29,212,215],{"className":213},[32,214],"pb-0","214.000+ YouTube weergaven",[11,217,113,220],{"className":218},[210,219],"case-kpi--orange",[29,221,223],{"className":222},[32],"Volledige branding en visuele identiteit",[11,225,113,228],{"className":226},[210,227],"case-k